root: ^Now what? Are you going to beg her?
^You just crawled back to her like a puppy.
^I... I need her. She makes me better.
^She makes you pathetic. You did a small mistake. She kick you in a heartbeat. Now you are after her, for what?. What if she had already forgotten about you?
^No. She didn't. She couldn't. She was just scared. We... I must prove her
^What if she had a new puppy to play with.
^Just... Shut Up! You know, what I am capable of without her.
^Being strong. That's what you are. We both know what you are. Do you think you can change it?
^No, but I can try. She can help me. She just needs to see I can change. I won't do that again. I won't hurt anyone, anymore.
^Yes, I am. Why all the hatred towards her, you can't take it do you, she just shackles you. You want to be unrestrained.
^Go on then. Hamper me if you can. We both know you'll be keen to unleash your fury when you're stuck.
^Her sweet smile... Her touch... A scent of a rose breeze.
^A disgusted face, a distant eye roll.
^I don't think I am ready. If you are right. Like if there is someone?
^You'll just bash that skull into pieces.
^This is it, we can check her beforehand.
